{"tid":2451461,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜隊友辣翻了！罕見開高衩　露出一雙「逆天長腿」驚呆粉","createTime":"2021-03-18T06:23:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T13:15:23.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"663c4481b91c2d2365621515dc18a4003b89d2a1","tid":2451461,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:23:21.000Z","msg":"南韓女團twice靠著亮眼的外型，與甜美的歌聲，從選秀節目出道後便一舉爆紅。其中台灣成員子瑜更是時常成為粉絲討論的話題。她的成員各個也是具有特色，近日適逢日籍成員Mina（名井南）透過官方平台曬出一系列美照，一雙逆天長腿更是火辣爆表。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/02/02/3011987-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F02%2F02%2F3011987-PH.jpg&h=0199f4b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE成員。（圖／翻攝自TWICEIG）<br />\n<br />\nMina近日曬出一系列美照，寫下「MINA BEST GIRL」只見照片中的她換上寶藍色的長洋裝，一頭金髮包成包頭，在陽光的照射下顯得更加亮眼。另外幾張則是她在不同拍攝時的照片，也換上像是細肩帶小可愛、一字領的黑色緊身洋裝，彷彿公主一般的美貌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/17/3069923-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F17%2F3069923-PH.jpg&h=bfeaac44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲Mina曬出美照。（圖／翻攝自TWICEIG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/17/3069922-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F17%2F3069922-PH.jpg&h=7e647384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n照片曝光後，粉絲紛紛嗨喊「MINA YOU&rsquo;RE SO PRETTY」、「MY ANGEL I AM DEAD ❤️」事實上，子瑜所屬的女團TWICE每位成員都表現都相當亮眼，日前更在官方頻道開播「TWICE REALITY &ldquo;TIME TO TWICE&rdquo; TWICE and the Chocolate Factory」影片，透過遊戲發覺成員們不同的一面。"},{"pid":"95afbdfee7f6690a1b72b47bc3d941d38f7c6e9c","tid":2451461,"uid":48783,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:24:14.000Z","msg":"生完仔仲正咗"},{"pid":"bbc032c95babcd5c53dcd7a31369217927bbfe04","tid":2451461,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:27:02.000Z","msg":"老婆真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完美女人"},{"pid":"8dbd229e0ee10fcfd82fc820b5f824bf49849657","tid":2451461,"uid":93096,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:29:06.000Z","msg":"乜嘢子魚隊友...冇名架..？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59ef454d252cb677258dfef94385ecef19991bd","tid":2451461,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8dbd229e0ee10fcfd82fc820b5f824bf49849657","tid":2451461,"uid":93096,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:29:06.000Z","msg":"乜嘢子魚隊友...冇名架..？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:30:02.000Z","msg":"台狗係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74dd01d9aa8593ecc7981ac3f71b2989222d34e2","tid":2451461,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95afbdfee7f6690a1b72b47bc3d941d38f7c6e9c","tid":2451461,"uid":48783,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:24:14.000Z","msg":"生完仔仲正咗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:30:17.000Z","msg":"無生過...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba6506ef9a55ee629e7fb4b7c4a610845a936ce","tid":2451461,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f59ef454d252cb677258dfef94385ecef19991bd","tid":2451461,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8dbd229e0ee10fcfd82fc820b5f824bf49849657","tid":2451461,"uid":93096,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:29:06.000Z","msg":"乜嘢子魚隊友...冇名架..？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:30:02.000Z","msg":"台狗係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T06:30:18.000Z","msg":"你咩狗...<img src=\"/assets/